'''Paffen''' was an illusion of an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] officer used by [[Akanah Norand Goss Pell|Akanah]] to further trick [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Jedi Master/Legends|Master]] [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]]. Luke attacked the illusionary Imperial and cut his arm off. After Luke and Akanah left [[Ialtra]] the body of Paffen dissipated into nothingness.

Paffen was created by the [[Dopplegänger]] [[Force power/Legends|Force power]] or a similar technique.

